claim: Flublok contains 45 micrograms (mcg) of HA per strain vs 15 mcg of HA per strain in a standard-dose influenza vaccine.
explanation: The image shows the header of a journal article from Elsevier’s Vaccine journal, including the Vaccine title, ScienceDirect reference, and journal homepage URL. The image contains only the journal cover/header and does not provide any information about Flublok or hemagglutinin (HA) content per strain, and therefore does not support the claim.
